title: 14. Esthetician Burn Out & How to Transition Your Career
description:
Hi friends, Lauren here. In this episode I am talking about getting burned out and how to transition your career within the skincare industry and the most popular career paths outside the treatment room. Please let me know what you think and feel free to DM us if you have any questions or want to discuss this topic further! Xo, Lo

Tess' Instagram @myestytessa.dermaplus + Tess' YouTube: Tess Zolly

Lauren's Instagram: @laurens.esthetics

Music by LiQwYd
